title: Searching for dedicated players for a new ranked team G+
body:
Making a new ranked team with a friend of mine and need three members for the following roles.

Top
Jungle
Support

Our goal would be to reach Masters/Challenger for the 2016 season and participate in competitive events. To do this we will need communication and dedication. Skype and microphone is required as well as a diversity when it comes to training times. You must also be ranked Gold or higher. If you are interested in joining please reply here or add me in game, Lman888.
